"DNS (Domain Name Service) is a distributed and hierarchical service mapping "
"names to IP addresses, and vice-versa. Specifically, it can turn a human-"
"friendly name such as <literal>www.eyrolles.com</literal> into the actual IP "
"address, <literal>213.244.11.247</literal>."
