"filename> e <filename>/etc/zshenv</filename>; <command>csh</command> usa "
"<filename>/etc/csh.cshrc</filename>, <filename>/etc/csh.login</filename> e "
"<filename>/etc/csh.logout</filename>. Le pagine di manuale per questi "
"programmi documentano quali file utilizzano."

